    • Method Detail

      • processSite

        java.util.Optional<org.json.JSONObject> processSite​(org.jsoup.nodes.Document document)
        Parses a document. It tries to find out whether there is an article in the document or not. If there is an article, it will fetch it and convert it into a JSON format.
        Parameters:
        document - Document to be parsed
        Returns:
        Optional of a JSONObject - it could be empty in case that no article has been found.
